[36m(TaskRunner pid=197332)[0m 
[36m(TaskRunner pid=197332)[0m First, we factor the denominator:
[36m(TaskRunner pid=197332)[0m \[ x^2 + x - 6 = (x + 3)(x - 2). \]
[36m(TaskRunner pid=197332)[0m 
[36m(TaskRunner pid=197332)[0m The denominator is zero when either \( x + 3 = 0 \) or \( x - 2 = 0 \). Solving these equations gives us:
[36m(TaskRunner pid=197332)[0m \[ x = -3 \quad \text{and} \quad x = 2. \]
[36m(TaskRunner pid=197332)[0m 
