[36m(TaskRunner pid=197332)[0m 
[36m(TaskRunner pid=197332)[0m 6. **Calculate the amount of money made from selling the remaining eggs:**
[36m(TaskRunner pid=197332)[0m    Janet sells the remaining eggs at $2 per egg.
